    16926 [label="ScancodeData:\nPer Fedora, this license is a modified version of the common MIT license,\nwith an additional advertising clause that makes it GPL-incompatible. It\nwas originally found at\nhttp://www.enlightenment.org/viewvc/e16/e/COPYING?revision=1.10 , but that\nURL is gone (they seem to have moved source control systems). The latest\navailable copy from enlightment.org\nhttp://trac.enlightenment.org/e/browser/trunk/E16/e/COPYING has been\npreserved here for reference."
